== Overview ==
[[Insight eSports]] is an electronic sports team and a portal of video game news. The organization alleges commitment to innovation and divulgation of Brazil's involvement in eSports, hosting teams in many of today's popular games.

On June 2012, Insight eSports created a team for League of Legends, picking up the members of Team Awake. The team has participated in many regional tournaments until its final roster in April 2013.

